Package demo.projects.test.framework.driver.abstraction

Class DriverWrapper

java.lang.Object
demo.projects.test.framework.driver.abstraction.DriverWrapper
Direct Known Subclasses:
Android, Browser
public abstract class DriverWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
Abstract Wrapper class for Selenium driver. To be extended by other classes implementing concrete drivers.
